channel.title: Mopar Scape Servers
channel.description:
Many servers run on with No-iP. You can choose (servername).no-ip.biz , (servername).no-ip.org or (servername).no-ip.info. I get frustrated when i type is a server name with .biz and it's .info or .org. I think to make it easier we should change the server iP's all to either .info .org or .biz. So you can't get confused.
What do you think about it?
